{"tid":1296814,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有的人活著，他已經死了。有的人死了，他還活著。","createTime":"2019-07-08T13:07:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T19:10:57.000Z","uid":159913,"like":87,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4a9b699c23e4543dd5db21ced06225b77c966851","tid":1296814,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:07:55.000Z","msg":"《有的人》臧克家<br />\n<br />\n有的人活著，他已經死了；<br />\n有的人死了，他還活著。<br />\n<br />\n有的人，騎在人民頭上：&ldquo;呵，我多偉大！&rdquo;<br />\n有的人，俯下身子給人民當牛馬。<br />\n<br />\n有的人，把名字刻入石頭想&ldquo;不朽&rdquo;；<br />\n有的人，情願作野草，等著地下的火燒。<br />\n<br />\n有的人，他活著別人就不能活；<br />\n有的人，他活著為了多數人更好地活。<br />\n<br />\n騎在人民頭上的，人民把他摔垮；<br />\n給人民作牛馬的，人民永遠記住他！<br />\n<br />\n把名字刻入石頭的，名字比屍首爛得更早；<br />\n只要春風吹到的地方，到處是青青的野草。<br />\n<br />\n他活著別人就不能活的人，他的下場可以看到；<br />\n他活著為了多數人更好活的人，群眾把他抬舉得很高，很高。"},{"pid":"fc0ebdc1e16c7b5d0f2e0a3f091bd9954bba0b1c","tid":1296814,"uid":159913,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:17:48.000Z","msg":"有的人，騎在人民頭上：&ldquo;呵，我多偉大！&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/translate/600/w1920h1080/20180701/FNnU-hespqry0642240.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ftranslate%2F600%2Fw1920h1080%2F20180701%2FFNnU-hespqry0642240.jpg&h=87fdd1d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d992b0318494da6081d922bba887ea6ad8b30c39","tid":1296814,"uid":159913,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:31:33.000Z","msg":"有的人，俯下身子給人民當牛馬。<br />\n<img src=\"https://external-preview.redd.it/zHmKI3z6fQYNIC0izMAJLXL_5__XoZU-eNgHKN9YYVM.jpg?width=960&amp;crop=smart&amp;auto=webp&amp;s=2af9e6924533fa3d4a36545add514bc03e669252\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fexternal-preview.redd.it%2FzHmKI3z6fQYNIC0izMAJLXL_5__XoZU-eNgHKN9YYVM.jpg%3Fwidth%3D960%26crop%3Dsmart%26auto%3Dwebp%26s%3D2af9e6924533fa3d4a36545add514bc03e669252&h=82d7aef7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc69868d1a0136926b0a1e7324f7297466e65f38","tid":1296814,"uid":240150,"